It's a simply shell to install hadoop and Hive, Pig... on CentOS 5 and 6 which 
can made hadoop installation easier and faster.

The hadoop installed with this script would be a fake distributed,
but you can comment some lines to use it with real distributed 
network.

It support lzo compressed data file by default, enjoy it.

Usage:
[root@localhost]#chmod +x this_shell_script.sh
[root@localhost]./this_shell_script.sh

Note: You must use root user to run this script, do not use sudo!!!